tafsir[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,"Alla woondirii pucci dogooji ƴekkitaali mum nane ngam sattude dokdu."
  100,2,"O woondiri pucci ɗi kolce mum kuɓɓata yiite siɗe memindirii e kaaƴe sabu sattude jangol e dow majje."
  100,3,"O woondiri pucci duggooji añɓe waktu subaka."
  100,4,"ɗi dilliniri kolce ɗe punndi."
  100,5,"ɗi ngoni hakkunde jaambareeɓe mum e dental añɓe."
  100,6,"Pellet aade ko kaɗoowo moƴƴere nde joomii mum faala e mum nde."
  100,7,"Kanko e haɗde mbo moƴƴere ko o ceediido, o waawah ɗum yeddude sabu ɓanngude ɗum."
  100,8,"Kanko ko no fantiniri nih yiɗde jawdi o lomatndi."
  100,9,"Mbela aade anndah kanko koomtiiɗo e aduna o wonde si Alla yaltanii wonɓe e genaale ummaade e leydi ngam haasboore e njoɓdi ma taw fiyaaku o wonah noɓe cikkiri nih woni?"
  100,10,"Yaltine ɓanngina ko woni e ɓerɗe ummaade e anniyaaji e piɓle e tanaa mum."
  100,11,"Pellet joom mum en ñande heen ko O kumpatiiɗo, hay ndiga wirnataako Mbo e fiyaaku jiyaaɓe Makko, ma O yoɓ ɓe ɗuum."
